title: Benicio del Toro will return for Guardians Of The Galaxy Vol. 2
text:
Benicio del Toro will return for Guardians Of The Galaxy Vol. 2 
Published By: TotalFilm.com - Today 
Zoe Saldana confirms that Benicio del Toro will reprise his role as the Collector in the Guardians Of The Galaxy sequel
